Introduction

Base URL: http://example-test.laravel.com

This documentation aims to provide all the information you need to work with our API.

As you scroll, you'll see code examples for working with the API in different programming languages in the dark area to the right (or as part of the content on mobile). You can switch the language used with the tabs at the top right (or from the nav menu at the top left on mobile).

Authenticating requests

This API is authenticated using a Bearer token.

Send your token in the Authorization header:

Authorization: Bearer <token>

You can retrieve the token by calling the login endpoint (POST /api/login).

Endpoints

用户登录接口

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/login" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"email\": \"owen01@example.com\",
    \"password\": \"sint\"
}"

const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/login"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "email": "owen01@example.com",
    "password": "sint"
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
Received response:
Request failed with error:


Tip: Check that you're properly connected to the network.
If you're a maintainer of ths API, verify that your API is running and you've enabled CORS.
You can check the Dev Tools console for debugging information.

Request      

POST api/login

Headers

Content-Type      

Example: application/json

Accept      

Example: application/json

Body Parameters

email   string   

Must be a valid email address. Example: owen01@example.com

password   string   

Example: sint

用户登出接口

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/logout" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/logout"
);

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());
Received response:
Request failed with error:


Tip: Check that you're properly connected to the network.
If you're a maintainer of ths API, verify that your API is running and you've enabled CORS.
You can check the Dev Tools console for debugging information.

获取当前登录用户信息

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request GET \
    --get "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/me" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/me"
);

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

Example response (401):

Show headers 
cache-control: no-cache, private
content-type: application/json
access-control-allow-origin: *

    "success": false,
    "code": 401,
    "message": "未授权，请先登录"
}

Request failed with error:

If you're a maintainer of ths API, verify that your API is running and you've enabled CORS.

创建新用户

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/users" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"name\": \"ifwxvqtaq\",
    \"email\": \"axel.hauck@example.net\",
    \"password\": \"Kc!~P=]s6nliv?T\",
    \"phone\": \"axtgsnubgqrosyc\"
}"

const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/users"
);

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "name": "ifwxvqtaq",
    "email": "axel.hauck@example.net",
    "password": "Kc!~P=]s6nliv?T",
    "phone": "axtgsnubgqrosyc"
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
Received response:
Request failed with error:


Tip: Check that you're properly connected to the network.
If you're a maintainer of ths API, verify that your API is running and you've enabled CORS.
You can check the Dev Tools console for debugging information.

Request      

POST api/users

Headers

Authorization      

Example: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}

Content-Type      

Example: application/json

Accept      

Example: application/json

Body Parameters

name   string   

Must not be greater than 255 characters. Example: ifwxvqtaq

email   string   

用户名（必填）. Must be a valid email address. Must not be greater than 255 characters. Example: axel.hauck@example.net

password   string   

邮箱（唯一）. Must be at least 8 characters. Example: Kc!~P=]s6nliv?T

phone   string  optional  

密码（必填，至少8位）. Must not be greater than 20 characters. Example: axtgsnubgqrosyc

roles   string[]  optional  

角色ID数组. The id of an existing record in the roles table.

更新用户信息

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request PUT \
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/users/dicta" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"name\": \"vbiofdzpkfbpjcbuvws\",
    \"password\": \"|M`%B;lm\",
    \"phone\": \"eynqlsakf\",
    \"is_active\": true
}"

const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/users/dicta"
);

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "name": "vbiofdzpkfbpjcbuvws",
    "password": "|M`%B;lm",
    "phone": "eynqlsakf",
    "is_active": true
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "PUT",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
Received response:

    --data "{
    \"name\": \"gbedv\",
    \"sku\": \"mfbfqcixotsiorbzskzpxla\",
    \"barcode\": \"necoxjxxvfwnnaryyieaft\",
    \"description\": \"Harum reprehenderit corrupti ad.\",
    \"image\": \"voluptatem\",
    \"purchase_price\": 2,
    \"sale_price\": 0,
    \"cost_price\": 48,
    \"min_stock\": 56,
    \"max_stock\": 12,
    \"is_active\": false
}"

const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/products"
);

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "name": "gbedv",
    "sku": "mfbfqcixotsiorbzskzpxla",
    "barcode": "necoxjxxvfwnnaryyieaft",
    "description": "Harum reprehenderit corrupti ad.",
    "image": "voluptatem",
    "purchase_price": 2,
    "sale_price": 0,
    "cost_price": 48,
    "min_stock": 56,
    "max_stock": 12,
    "is_active": false
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());

Request      

POST api/products

Headers

Authorization      

Example: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}

Content-Type      

Example: application/json

Accept      

Example: application/json

Body Parameters

category_id   string  optional  

The id of an existing record in the product_categories table.

name   string   

产品分类. Must not be greater than 255 characters. Example: gbedv

sku   string   

产品名称（必填）. Must not be greater than 255 characters. Example: mfbfqcixotsiorbzskzpxla

barcode   string  optional  

SKU编码（唯一）. Must not be greater than 255 characters. Example: necoxjxxvfwnnaryyieaft

description   string  optional  

条形码（唯一）. Example: Harum reprehenderit corrupti ad.

image   string  optional  

产品描述. Example: voluptatem

unit_id   string  optional  

产品图片. The id of an existing record in the units table.

purchase_price   number  optional  

计量单位. Must be at least 0. Example: 2

sale_price   number  optional  

采购价. Must be at least 0. Example: 0

cost_price   number  optional  

销售价. Must be at least 0. Example: 48

min_stock   integer  optional  

成本价. Must be at least 0. Example: 56

max_stock   integer  optional  

最低库存. Must be at least 0. Example: 12

is_active   boolean  optional  

最高库存. Example: false

Must not be greater than 20 characters. Example: ezqpxuluixwlzjjdhos

email   string  optional  

Must be a valid email address. Must not be greater than 255 characters. Example: mlarkin@example.org

region_id   string  optional  

The id of an existing record in the regions table.

address   string  optional  

Must not be greater than 500 characters. Example: wmcdfc

tax_number   string  optional  

Must not be greater than 255 characters. Example: vmxziidkvl

bank_name   string  optional  

Must not be greater than 255 characters. Example: pos

bank_account   string  optional  

Must not be greater than 255 characters. Example: kgioxncrvvywzhkaclbtk

rating   string  optional  

Example: C

Must be one of:
  • A
  • B
  • C
  • D
credit_limit   number  optional  

Must be at least 0. Example: 10

payment_days   integer  optional

is_active   boolean  optional

Request      

POST api/purchase-settlements

Headers

Authorization      

Example: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}

Content-Type      

Example: application/json

Accept      

Example: application/json

Body Parameters

supplier_id   string   

The id of an existing record in the suppliers table. Example: perferendis

settlement_date   string   

供应商ID（必填）. Must be a valid date. Example: 2025-12-24T08:09:21

currency_id   string  optional  

结算日期（必填）. The id of an existing record in the currencies table.

remark   string  optional  

币种ID. Example: possimus

items   object[]   

备注. Must have at least 1 items.
reference_type   string   

结算明细（至少一条）. Example: purchase_return

Must be one of:
  • purchase_order
  • purchase_return
reference_id   integer   

关联类型. Example: 3

remark   string  optional  

关联单据ID. Example: enim

Request      

POST api/process-routes

Headers

Authorization      

Example: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}

Content-Type      

Example: application/json

Accept      

Example: application/json

Body Parameters

product_id   string   

The id of an existing record in the products table. Example: velit

version   string   

产品ID（必填）. Must not be greater than 50 characters. Example: hqlckbhwkuyvczadqhwqk

effective_date   string   

版本号（必填）. Must be a valid date. Example: 2025-12-24T08:09:21

expiry_date   string  optional  

生效日期（必填）. Must be a valid date. Must be a date after effective_date. Example: 2080-12-09

is_default   boolean  optional  

失效日期. Example: true

is_active   boolean  optional  

是否默认版本. Example: true

description   string  optional  

是否激活. Example: Et dolore et aliquid est mollitia eaque mollitia sed.

steps   object[]   

描述. Must have at least 1 items.
step_name   string   

工序步骤（至少一个）. Must not be greater than 255 characters. Example: qvvbvixspayzjudo

step_code   string  optional  

工序名称. Must not be greater than 100 characters. Example: mmgwnehcej

sequence   integer   

工序编码. Must be at least 1. Example: 32

work_center   string  optional  

工序顺序. Must not be greater than 100 characters. Example: qqvphos

standard_time   number  optional  

工作中心. Must be at least 0. Example: 68

setup_time   number  optional  

标准工时. Must be at least 0. Example: 48

queue_time   number  optional  

准备时间. Must be at least 0. Example: 76

move_time   number  optional  

排队时间. Must be at least 0. Example: 15

description   string  optional  

转移时间. Example: Sunt aut iure reprehenderit voluptatem sit consectetur sunt magni.

remark   string  optional  

工序描述. Example: labore

Accept      

Example: application/json

Body Parameters

sales_order_id   string  optional  

The id of an existing record in the sales_orders table.

plan_date   string   

关联销售订单. Must be a valid date. Example: 2025-12-24T08:09:21

start_date   string   

计划日期（必填）. Must be a valid date. Example: 2025-12-24T08:09:21

end_date   string   

开始日期（必填）. Must be a valid date. Must be a date after start_date. Example: 2091-03-27

warehouse_id   string   

结束日期（必填）. The id of an existing record in the warehouses table. Example: dolorem

remark   string  optional  

仓库（必填）. Example: illum

items   object[]   

备注. Must have at least 1 items.
product_id   string   

明细项（必填）. The id of an existing record in the products table. Example: blanditiis

bom_id   string  optional  

产品ID. The id of an existing record in the boms table.

process_route_id   string  optional  

BOM ID. The id of an existing record in the process_routes table.

planned_quantity   integer   

工艺路线ID. Must be at least 1. Example: 79

planned_start_date   string   

计划数量. Must be a valid date. Example: 2025-12-24T08:09:21

planned_end_date   string   

计划开始日期. Must be a valid date. Must be a date after items.*.planned_start_date. Example: 2094-06-24

priority   integer  optional  

计划结束日期. Must be at least 0. Example: 29

remark   string  optional  

优先级. Example: necessitatibus

Request      

POST api/work-orders

Headers

Authorization      

Example: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}

Content-Type      

Example: application/json

Accept      

Example: application/json

Body Parameters

production_plan_id   string  optional  

The id of an existing record in the production_plans table.

production_plan_item_id   string  optional  

生产计划ID. The id of an existing record in the production_plan_items table.

product_id   string   

生产计划明细ID. The id of an existing record in the products table. Example: omnis

bom_id   string  optional  

产品ID（必填）. The id of an existing record in the boms table.

process_route_id   string  optional  

BOM ID. The id of an existing record in the process_routes table.

warehouse_id   string   

工艺路线ID. The id of an existing record in the warehouses table. Example: accusamus

quantity   integer   

仓库ID（必填）. Must be at least 1. Example: 33

start_date   string   

生产数量（必填）. Must be a valid date. Example: 2025-12-24T08:09:21

planned_end_date   string   

开始日期（必填）. Must be a valid date. Must be a date after start_date. Example: 2034-06-26

assigned_to   string  optional  

计划结束日期. The id of an existing record in the users table.

remark   string  optional  

分配人. Example: rerum

  • general
  • adjustment
  • closing

备注. Must have at least 2 items.
account_id   string   

明细项（至少2条）. The id of an existing record in the chart_of_accounts table. Example: exercitationem

Must be one of:
  • debit
  • credit
amount   number   

借贷方向. Must be at least 0. Example: 3

summary   string  optional  

金额. Example: dolorem

reference_type   string  optional  

摘要. Example: aspernatur

reference_id   integer  optional  

关联业务类型. Example: 4

reference_no   string  optional  

关联业务ID. Example: ratione

sequence   integer  optional  

关联业务编号. Must be at least 0. Example: 13

received_amount   number  optional

remark   string  optional

创建工作流

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/workflows" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"name\": \"wteeuizdyvozacl\",
    \"code\": \"velit\",
    \"type\": \"purchase_order\",
    \"description\": \"Velit nisi autem qui ex.\",
    \"is_active\": true,
    \"nodes\": [
        {
            \"node_name\": \"urczfcbrh\",
            \"node_type\": \"condition\",
            \"sequence\": 63,
            \"approval_type\": \"any\",
            \"timeout_hours\": 70,
            \"is_required\": false,
            \"remark\": \"nemo\"
        }
    ]
}"

const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/workflows"
);

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "name": "wteeuizdyvozacl",
    "code": "velit",
    "type": "purchase_order",
    "description": "Velit nisi autem qui ex.",
    "is_active": true,
    "nodes": [
        {
            "node_name": "urczfcbrh",
            "node_type": "condition",
            "sequence": 63,
            "approval_type": "any",
            "timeout_hours": 70,
            "is_required": false,
            "remark": "nemo"
        }
    ]
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());

Request      

POST api/workflows

Headers

Authorization      

Example: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}

Content-Type      

Example: application/json

Accept      

Example: application/json

Body Parameters

name   string   

Must not be greater than 255 characters. Example: wteeuizdyvozacl

code   string   

工作流名称（必填）. Example: velit

type   string   

工作流编码（唯一）. Example: purchase_order

Must be one of:
  • purchase_order
  • sales_order
  • expense
  • work_order
  • production_plan
description   string  optional  

类型. Example: Velit nisi autem qui ex.

is_active   boolean  optional  

描述. Example: true

nodes   object[]   

是否激活. Must have at least 1 items.
node_name   string   

节点数组（至少一个）. Must not be greater than 255 characters. Example: urczfcbrh

node_type   string   

节点名称. Example: condition

Must be one of:
  • start
  • approval
  • condition
  • end
sequence   integer   

节点类型. Must be at least 1. Example: 63

approval_type   string  optional  

节点顺序. Example: any

Must be one of:
  • single
  • all
  • any
approver_config   object  optional  

审批类型.

condition_config   object  optional  

审批人配置.

next_nodes   object  optional  

条件配置.

timeout_hours   integer  optional  

下一节点. Must be at least 0. Example: 70

is_required   boolean  optional  

超时时间. Example: false

remark   string  optional  

是否必须. Example: nemo

创建自定义报表定义

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/custom-reports" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"name\": \"wony\",
    \"code\": \"temporibus\",
    \"category\": \"inventory\",
    \"description\": \"Eos voluptatem omnis quia voluptatem quia.\",
    \"query_config\": [],
    \"display_config\": [],
    \"is_active\": true
}"

const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/custom-reports"
);

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "name": "wony",
    "code": "temporibus",
    "category": "inventory",
    "description": "Eos voluptatem omnis quia voluptatem quia.",
    "query_config": [],
    "display_config": [],
    "is_active": true
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
Received response:

Request      

POST api/custom-reports

Headers

Authorization      

Example: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}

Content-Type      

Example: application/json

Accept      

Example: application/json

Body Parameters

name   string   

Must not be greater than 255 characters. Example: wony

code   string   

报表名称. Example: temporibus

category   string   

报表编码（唯一）. Example: inventory

Must be one of:
  • sales
  • purchase
  • inventory
  • financial
  • custom
description   string  optional  

报表分类. Example: Eos voluptatem omnis quia voluptatem quia.

query_config   object   

报表描述.

display_config   object   

查询配置（JSON）.

is_active   boolean  optional  

显示配置（JSON）. Example: true

Accept      

Example: application/json

Body Parameters

user_id   string   

The id of an existing record in the users table. Example: et

type   string   

目标用户ID（必填）. Example: financial

Must be one of:
  • system
  • approval
  • order
  • inventory
  • financial
title   string   

通知类型. Must not be greater than 255 characters. Example: wjbvp

content   string   

标题（必填）. Example: rem

channel   string  optional  

内容（必填）. Example: system

Must be one of:
  • system
  • email
  • sms
  • push
priority   string  optional  

发送渠道. Example: urgent

Must be one of:
  • low
  • normal
  • high
  • urgent
reference_type   string  optional  

优先级. Example: sed

reference_id   integer  optional  

关联业务类型. Example: 8

reference_no   string  optional  

关联业务ID. Example: est

data   object  optional  

关联业务编号.

Request      

PUT api/notification-templates/{id}

PATCH api/notification-templates/{id}

Headers

Authorization      

Example: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}

Content-Type      

Example: application/json

Accept      

Example: application/json

URL Parameters

id   string   

The ID of the notification template. Example: doloremque

Body Parameters

code   string  optional  
name   string   

Must not be greater than 255 characters. Example: pmypewiunhfm

type   string   

Example: approval

Must be one of:
  • system
  • approval
  • order
  • inventory
  • financial
channel   string   

Example: email

Must be one of:
  • system
  • email
  • sms
  • push
subject   string  optional  

Must not be greater than 255 characters. Example: ggjgcpzgdsif

content   string   

Example: architecto

variables   object  optional  
is_active   boolean  optional  

Example: true

删除通知模板

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request DELETE \
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/notification-templates/totam" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/notification-templates/totam"
);

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "DELETE",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

获取操作日志列表

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request GET \
    --get "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/operation-logs" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/operation-logs"
);

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());
